This is the erlang API to ConfD
To build and use - erl, erlc, confd and confdc must be in the
user PATH

# make

in this topdir will build and make econfd. 

econfd is meant to be dropped into an existing otp lib structure.

examples are found in the 'examples' dir.

documentation is written in edoc, and the generated html is found in
the 'doc' directory.


